node.text:
Are you ready for the penultimate @contitourgold meet of the season?

We've got two days of action ahead of us – starting with the men's shot put, the Ivan Ivancevic Memorial, on Monday 13 September and the in-stadium programme on Tuesday 14 September.

Watch all the action LIVE on the World Athletics YouTube channel or your local broadcaster.

#ContinentalTourGold #trackandfield #athletics #zagrebmeeting

🚨 WORLD RECORD 🚨

Senbere Teferi 🇪🇹 breaks the world record for the women's 5k, clocking 14:29 to take the win at the #adizero Road To Records event!

What a day for women's road running 💫

#Athletics #WorldAthletics #WorldRecord #RoadRunning #TrackAndField

🚨 WORLD RECORD 🚨

Agnes Jebet Tirop 🇰🇪 smashes the women’s 10k world record (for a women-only race) in a time of 30:01 at the #adizero Road to Records event!

#Athletics #WorldAthletics #WorldRecord #RoadRunning
